WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:06.240
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:07.759
for joining me again tonight. We're

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:10.719
going to go over some of the things the

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:12.719
Lord showed us last night.

00:00:10.719 --> 00:00:14.639
It was a little different prayer

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:16.560
time for what I was seeing about

00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:18.640
the Ring of Fire. And the Lord said,

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:21.680
"Great earthquakes on the

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:23.680
West Coast."I saw

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:26.560
major earthquakes getting ready to take

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:29.039
place last night on the West Coast, and

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.720
it would shake the nations. The

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:34.480
Lord said he was going to shake the

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:37.040
nations.

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:39.120
What was interesting about this is as I

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:42.800
was looking into the spirit concerning

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:47.120
the water, I saw lakes beginning to get

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:49.919
really hot, and I could see

00:00:47.120 --> 00:00:54.078
some kind of

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:56.160
green algae because the water was above-average

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:59.120
warm.

00:00:56.160 --> 00:01:01.919
It was producing this green, murky-looking

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:03.680
algae through it, and people

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:06.240
didn't notice it at first; they just

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:09.360
thought the water was warm.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:11.600
But the temperature kept rising.

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:13.439
I could see certain temperatures

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:17.360
of 70-some degrees—70

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:21.279
then 80—and it went

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:24.640
all the way up to 92 degrees.

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:29.439
It was a lake, a fresh body of

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:32.880
water, not an ocean. I saw

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:36.320
inland, towards the

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:38.479
Portland area, Seattle, all throughout that area,

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:42.798
that the water would

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:45.119
get hot and the fish didn't like the

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:48.479
temperature and they were dying. I

00:01:45.119 --> 00:01:51.200
could see them all coming up to the

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:54.880
surface because the water temperature

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:58.000
was too warm. The only way

00:01:54.880 --> 00:02:01.439
I could see was that there was some

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:04.000
kind of magma

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:06.719
from volcanic activity coming up under it.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:08.479
It was warming things.

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:11.519
I don't know if there's an active

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:15.599
volcano in those areas in the past, but

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:18.319
wherever this was, the lava,

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:19.920
the magma was coming up

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:26.000
and making

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:28.400
the water get warm.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:30.480
Like I said, they were

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:33.120
testing it. I could see them testing

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:34.799
the water temperature, and I saw on

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:36.560
the thermostat—kind of like what you

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:38.160
have on an air conditioner how they

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:40.160
point it at the air conditioning vent

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:41.519
ducts

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:43.359
and they'll be able to say, "Well,

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:44.879
the air is coming out

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:47.040
at this temperature"—well, they were doing

00:02:44.879 --> 00:02:50.399
that to the water and they were testing

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:53.120
it, but the fish were dying. And then they

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:55.840
said, "Notice the animals."The

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:57.760
animals knew, and the Lord said in

00:02:55.840 --> 00:03:00.800
the prayer time, "I have put it in the

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:04.560
animals to know when danger is about to happen."And

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:07.200
he said, "A great shaking

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:11.680
will bring them to their

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:14.000
knees to bring my bride to my side."And

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:15.920
I saw a shaking

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:19.120
in Japan.

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:22.720
The Lord specifically said,

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:25.680
"The Ring of Fire."He said, "The plates

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:28.000
are shifting and there will be great

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:31.440
earthquakes in the days ahead."I saw

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:33.519
them be record numbers—lots

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:36.319
of earthquakes, big earthquakes,

00:03:33.519 --> 00:03:39.680
small earthquakes all happening—and it

00:03:36.319 --> 00:03:42.560
would become very active. And I saw a

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:45.760
split in the earth where you could see

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:48.080
deep down in there from the edge, like

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:50.159
the movie San Andreas, like a movie

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:51.920
Hollywood would produce where

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:54.079
the ground would split and

00:03:51.920 --> 00:03:55.760
the earth would fall in. You

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:57.280
could look down for a long way

00:03:55.760 --> 00:04:00.000
and you could fall in and lose your

00:03:57.280 --> 00:04:03.200
life. That's how far it was. I saw the

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:05.360
earth moving, opening up.

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:07.280
That was our

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:08.560
prayer time last night. And the Lord

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:10.720
warned us, "There's going to be

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:12.959
great shakings in the days ahead. I'm

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:15.120
going to shake the Ring of Fire. I'm

00:04:12.959 --> 00:04:18.959
going to shake the Ring of Fire."And I

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:21.600
saw droughts. I saw major droughts

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:23.840
coming.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:25.840
What else

00:04:23.840 --> 00:04:27.440
was there? Because that prayer time went

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:30.080
on a long time last night. We prayed for

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:32.080
almost three hours again.

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:36.719
Then we were praying for President Trump,

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:40.320
praying for this weekend, praying for

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:42.160
the Clarity Act, praying for Amy Coney

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:46.800
Barrett

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:49.199
because I saw a paranoia

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:52.160
coming on her again last night. I saw

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:54.960
her mind was being affected by demonic

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:56.800
influence; she was paranoid and she

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:59.680
acts like—and some people say

00:04:56.800 --> 00:05:01.600
she's schizophrenic—and the Lord said, "No,

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:03.759
she's not schizophrenic. This is a

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:07.039
spirit tormenting her. It's a spirit

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:09.680
of fear."I saw her peeking out the

00:05:07.039 --> 00:05:13.199
blinds again, and I saw her looking

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:15.919
behind corners. She was acting like

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:19.280
she was losing it, and her husband

00:05:15.919 --> 00:05:22.240
left her, and

00:05:19.280 --> 00:05:24.559
I saw a spirit trying to influence

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:26.639
her big time.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:29.520
Specifically, that she didn't want to be

00:05:26.639 --> 00:05:32.000
a Supreme Court judge anymore. She

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:33.599
said, "I resign. I don't want this. I

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:36.560
want to move on with my life. This is

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:39.360
not what I want."The torment

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:42.479
was so bad she couldn't sleep at night.

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:44.240
I saw her in her bed laying there, and

00:05:42.479 --> 00:05:46.159
she could not sleep because she was

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:48.479
listening for her children, thinking

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:51.039
that her children were in danger,

00:05:48.479 --> 00:05:53.758
listening for any kind of

00:05:51.039 --> 00:05:55.440
sound outside or any

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:58.479
kind of noise because she thought

00:05:55.440 --> 00:06:00.320
her life was in danger all the time.

00:05:58.479 --> 00:06:02.000
So much so that she started losing her

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:04.240
hair from the stress.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:07.039
Her hair

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:09.120
is thinning. The Lord

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:11.280
said, "I saw in the vision

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:13.360
her hair started coming out in clumps,

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:15.840
but she didn't want to make it public.

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:17.120
Her

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:19.679
roots were dying. Something was happening."I

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:23.600
saw that last night

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:26.319
and I felt sorry for her. The way

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:29.120
her eyes looked, she looked so

00:06:26.319 --> 00:06:31.039
uneasy, like it was killing her

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:32.720
from within.

00:06:31.039 --> 00:06:36.400
The position was killing her from

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:38.240
within, but it was demonic influence.

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:40.560
And then the Lord said, "Pray for

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:42.319
Clarence Thomas for his

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:43.680
health. Pray for this and the Supreme

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:45.520
Court judges."But this one was

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:47.280
interesting because it was about her. So

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:48.400
I just see in part here. I

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.919
don't know what that's about. Maybe

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:52.318
she's going to deal with some stuff.

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:53.359
Maybe she's not. I'm

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:55.039
sure she's never going to come on there

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:56.080
and tell you she's losing her hair, and

00:06:55.039 --> 00:06:58.000
she's never going to tell you if

00:06:56.080 --> 00:06:59.599
she's having marriage problems until you

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:01.199
see it in the news or the tabloids

00:06:59.599 --> 00:07:03.919
saying, "Oh, they're getting a divorce."I

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:06.400
don't know. I

00:07:03.919 --> 00:07:08.318
pray that's not true. I pray I miss it.

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:10.239
That is a very sad situation to see

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:12.639
anybody living in that kind of fear. No

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:14.479
matter if they're right or left,

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:17.039
you don't want to see people

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:19.440
suffering. It's

00:07:17.039 --> 00:07:22.159
hard. And so, that's what the Lord

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:23.680
showed me. I saw that, and then we

00:07:22.160 --> 00:07:26.160
were praying

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:29.120
over her, and we're praying over

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:33.280
South Korea for a rising up, and

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:35.759
a stirring in Australia

00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:39.840
to wake up the

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:42.479
people. And I saw a big clock, and I

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:46.159
could see

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:49.039
the time was up on a big grandfather

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:51.759
clock. But behind the grandfather clock

00:07:49.039 --> 00:07:53.520
was a great light shining upon it.

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:56.879
And the Lord said,

00:07:53.520 --> 00:08:00.960
"Time's up. Time's

00:07:56.879 --> 00:08:04.160
up."I'm

00:08:00.960 --> 00:08:07.840
coming. Time's up. And I heard this,

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:09.680
"Bong, bong, bong, bong,"as the

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:11.599
hour... whenever a grandfather

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:14.879
clock sounds beautiful, whenever it

00:08:11.599 --> 00:08:17.280
starts the chimes, but it

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:20.080
wasn't like chimes—like a "bing, bing, bing."It

00:08:17.280 --> 00:08:22.719
was a very deep

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:26.318
sound like Big Ben,

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:29.120
like a big loud noise.

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:30.639
I

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.479
don't know if Big Ben chimes,

00:08:30.639 --> 00:08:33.839
but like Big

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:34.560
Ben, you know?

00:08:34.559 --> 00:08:40.159
Does Big Ben chime? I don't know. But

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:44.079
that's what I assume it would sound

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:48.000
like. Okay, so I saw that. What

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:50.720
else did we see? Oh, a hurricane hitting

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:51.839
the East Coast—a major

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:54.560
hurricane. Well, you say, "Well, it's

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:57.920
hurricane season, Brandon."Well,

00:08:54.560 --> 00:09:00.880
duh. We have hurricanes in this. I

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:03.920
saw a hurricane hitting the Miami and West

00:09:00.880 --> 00:09:06.480
Palm Beach area, and I continued to

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:09.120
see a hurricane hitting the Miami and West

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:13.440
Palm Beach area and it was catastrophic.

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:16.560
A major hurricane, category three or four,

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:19.680
and it hit the side. What was

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:22.319
interesting was the surge

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:25.439
was abnormal.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:27.680
The

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:31.360
water came inland a long way and it was

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:34.079
deep, and people were surfboarding,

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:37.440
like laying on top

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:40.160
of the surfboard using it for a

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:42.240
boat. I saw them doing paddleboard.

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:46.240
They were trying to get from point

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:49.279
A to point B on their bellies, trying to

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:52.080
go through the towns as I saw water.

00:09:49.279 --> 00:09:54.959
They didn't evacuate, obviously, but I saw

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:59.279
them and I saw a major hurricane

00:09:54.959 --> 00:10:01.359
coming in that area.

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:03.360
I don't know why it

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:06.160
would be significant about that any more

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:08.000
than what any of the others are, but the

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:11.600
Lord showed it to me. So, I just tell

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:12.800
you what I see.

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:14.560
What else?

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:19.519
You saw the dormant seeds.

00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:22.160
I saw dormant seeds in the church.

00:10:19.519 --> 00:10:24.079
This was

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:26.399
interesting because,

00:10:24.079 --> 00:10:28.160
being in the country most of my

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:30.640
life with my family, there are a

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:33.519
bunch of farmers. Grandpa and them

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:36.160
would till the fields with

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:38.560
the big disc and they would take their

00:10:36.160 --> 00:10:40.719
John Deeres and run

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:43.680
those fields over and plow

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:46.640
the field up. But there were no big

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:49.279
tire tracks in those fields after

00:10:46.640 --> 00:10:51.839
the disc tilled the field up. You

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:53.360
didn't see big tire tracks because the

00:10:51.839 --> 00:10:55.279
tractor was ahead and it went ahead, and

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:58.480
they didn't go back over it and mess up

00:10:55.279 --> 00:11:01.439
the land unless

00:10:58.480 --> 00:11:05.519
they were dragging something, right? But

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:08.320
I saw tire tracks inside of the field

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:12.320
that was sown,

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:14.880
and it was squished down, and all the

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:17.040
tire tracks had messed up where the

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:21.600
field had been planted.

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:24.480
All of a sudden, I saw it was so dry,

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:26.320
and those seeds that you thought were

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.920
dormant came up out of the

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:32.160
dryness when rain started coming on

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:34.319
them. And I saw the tire tracks start to

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:36.000
have plants grow up inside the tire

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:37.519
track.

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:40.320
I know it's symbolic. I don't know

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:42.399
what that means, but it was

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:47.240
interesting because the tire

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:47.240
tracks were getting fruit

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:53.839
and all of a sudden the dormant seeds

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:57.200
become life.

00:11:53.839 --> 00:11:59.360
I thought that was kind of neat. Is

00:11:57.200 --> 00:12:01.040
that

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:02.959
it?

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:05.199
Yeah. And you saw a wildfire.

00:12:02.959 --> 00:12:07.359
Japan,.

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:10.560
Yeah, I saw a lot of wildfires. And the

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:12.320
Lord said major wildfires in Colorado.

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:14.880
And he brought that up again. He was

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:17.600
saying that there was arson—people

00:12:14.880 --> 00:12:21.120
starting fires on purpose.

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:24.160
Major fires were being set on purpose,

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:27.440
deliberately.

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:31.199
I don't know why,

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:33.920
people are just nuts. So,

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:36.720
we saw that praying over it. Did we

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:37.040
see anything else about Zelensky?

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:38.560
No.

00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:39.439
Was that last night or the night before?

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.279
Night before.

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:43.360
Okay. So, we saw Zelensky. We saw that

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:46.920
about him and all and

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:46.920
praying over that.

00:12:48.160 --> 00:12:51.040
You said you saw something concerning

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:52.319
Trump.

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:54.880
Yeah. I don't want to talk about that.

00:12:52.320 --> 00:12:56.480
Okay.

00:12:56.959 --> 00:13:01.439
Portland, Oregon.

00:12:58.160 --> 00:13:03.120
Yeah, Portland, Oregon.

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:06.519
So, we pray over Trump, we pray

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:06.519
over his family.

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:12.480
That's it on that. So, there are highlights.

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:14.240
For those of you who say, 'Well, I don't

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:16.240
have time to pray,'I give you the

00:13:14.240 --> 00:13:17.920
highlights. You don't miss anything here.

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:19.279
I'm going to

00:13:17.920 --> 00:13:21.199
try to do it at the very beginning like I

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:22.639
just did for you. So, for those that

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:24.880
